2010-11-5    cwinux@gmail.com   v1.2.1
store模块的CwxBinLogFile类，修改sid的折半查找算法的bug，缺少+-1，api为：
int CwxBinLogFile::seek(CwxBinLogCursor& cursor, CWX_UINT8 ucMode);